---
// Section 7 — Pricing (stated, not sold). Not a table. Free tier first.
// Accent is never a text color, so the price is emphasised by weight only.
---

<section aria-labelledby="pricing-title" class="border-t border-hairline">
  <div class="mx-0 max-w-[720px] px-6 py-16 md:pl-20 md:pr-8 md:py-24">
    <h2 id="pricing-title" class="sr-only">Pricing</h2>
    <p class="max-w-[48ch] text-body text-text-primary">
      Three scenarios free. No card, no signup wall.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-3 max-w-[48ch] text-body text-text-primary">
      After that, <span class="font-semibold">$1.99 a week</span> if you want the rest.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-6 max-w-[54ch] text-body text-text-secondary">
      Cancel whenever. We would rather you stayed because you keep losing to the
      landlord.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
